Password: String

ðŸ”¹ Login: Class
Handles user login for donors and admins.

UserName: String

Password: String

ðŸ”¹ PatientRequest: Class
Represents a blood request made for a patient.

RequestId: Integer

PatientName: String

BloodGroup: String

RequiredUnits: Integer

HospitalName: String

DoctorName: String

ContactNo: Long/String

RequestDate: String

Status: String (Pending, Fulfilled, Cancelled)

ðŸ”¹ DonationRecord: Class
Tracks each successful blood donation.

DonationId: Integer

